Notes: 
1. To start, a third party platform need to be used; 
2. Click the button "Select an area" when you have entered the Go Chess Game Page; 
3. For the time to select an area, the chessboard area will be automatically identified. If the identification is not accurate, you can manually adjust it. That will be OK when the green box basically overlaps the chessboard sideline; 
4. When it's your turn to play chess, click the button "Start Service", and start playing when the configuration of the game is done; 
5. You need to beat the timer to confirm when you have laid a piece.
